: "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1d18/d15e/502238_mini.png?m=1650606914", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1d18/d15e/502238_normal.png?m=1650606914", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1d18/d15e/502238_large.png?m=1650606914", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1d18/d15e/502238_xlarge.png?m=1650606914", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1d18/d15e/502238_xlarge.png?m=1650606914", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1d18/d15e/502238_xlarge.png?m=1650606914", "created": 1596500386, "last_modified": 1650606914}, "last_reply_by": "EvilDevilJin", "last_touched": 1654156363, "title": "mac 下代理软件的选择", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/857123", "created": 1654238987, "deleted": 0, "content": "楼主最开始用的是 shadowsocksX-NG ，后来由于增加了 vmess 的服务器就换成了大名鼎鼎的 clashX ；接着，看了 V2EX 上的一些帖子换成了据说更好用的 clashX PRO ，同样是免费的，但是我发现 PRO 不是开源的就换回 clashX 了\r\n\r\n最近高强度网上冲浪发现很多问题，不知道是和 mac 有关还是 clashX 自身的问题，包括 pppoe 拨号上网时切换“设置系统代理”会失效（重启恢复）、同一个服务器在 clashX 中无法连接但是用 shadowsocksX-NG 和手机上的 shadowrocket 都能连接\r\n\r\n目前有点迷茫，大家都用的哪款呢（这个是可以讨论的吗，不可以的话麻烦 mod 删帖🙏🏻）", "content_rendered": "<p>楼主最开始用的是 shadowsocksX-NG ，后来由于增加了 vmess 的服务器就换成了大名鼎鼎的 clashX ；接着，看了 V2EX 上的一些帖子换成了据说更好用的 clashX PRO ，同样是免费的，但是我发现 PRO 不是开源的就换回 clashX 了</p>\n<p>最近高强度网上冲浪发现很多问题，不知道是和 mac 有关还是 clashX 自身的问题，包括 pppoe 拨号上网时切换“设置系统代理”会失效（重启恢复）、同一个服务器在 clashX 中无法连接但是用 shadowsocksX-NG 和手机上的 shadowrocket 都能连接</p>\n<p>目前有点迷茫，大家都用的哪款呢（这个是可以讨论的吗，不可以的话麻烦 mod 删帖🙏🏻）</p>\n", "last_modified": 1654239040, "replies": 35, "id": 857123}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_large.png?m=1584400459", "name": "xiaomi", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_normal.png?m=1584400459", "title": "小米", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/xiaomi", "topics": 730, "footer": "", "header": "关于小米公司出品的各种智能硬件的使用讨论", "title_alternative": "Xiaomi", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/301a/d0e3/834_mini.png?m=1584400459", "stars": 289, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 834, "parent_node_name": "android"}, "member": {"id": 535448, "username": "GCP", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/GCP", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/916e/9d3e/535448_mini.png?m=1653640700", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/916e/9d3e/535448_normal.png?m=1653640700", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/916e/9d3e/535448_large.png?m=1653640700", "created": 1614618074, "last_modified": 1653640700}, "last_reply_by": "xdwmxx", "last_touched": 1654322688, "title": "超过 30 岁戴小米手环会不会显得幼稚？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/857218", "created": 1654311750, "deleted": 0, "content": "想买个小巧点的手环，续航比 Apple Watch 强，睡觉戴着也还行，考虑小米手环 7\n\n年纪大了，平时正装居多，戴这个会不会不太合适？", "content_rendered": "想买个小巧点的手环，续航比 Apple Watch 强，睡觉戴着也还行，考虑小米手环 7<br /><br />年纪大了，平时正装居多，戴这个会不会不太合适？", "last_modified": 1654320780, "replies": 35, "id": 857218}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 18521, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2172, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 467848, "username": "Atlanta2020", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Atlanta2020", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/782a8fd2bb268136629d60131fabd65c?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/782a8fd2bb268136629d60131fabd65c?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/782a8fd2bb268136629d60131fabd65c?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1580826170, "last_modified": 1580826170}, "last_reply_by": "hahasong", "last_touched": 1654322635, "title": "明天就是发布会了，我的 mbp 今天送到了，为什么我有种不详的预感，怎么办啊？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/857213", "created": 1654308296, "deleted": 0, "content": "坏了，5 月份买的 mbp ，在 6 月 5 号，今天送到了。本来的预期送达日期是 7 月 9 号，到 8 月底。\r\n我估摸着如果发布会发了新品就退换更合适的。但是，今天突然送到了。\r\n出于激动，我还拆开来看了下，14 寸 10 核 16G 内存 1T 硬盘的 mbp 。\r\n有一点点重，但是看起来倒是挺小巧的。观感还行，可是明天就是发布会了啊，明天应该不会有 M2 的 mbp 吧？有点害怕。\r\n\r\n大家有什么想法么？", "content_rendered": "<p>坏了，5 月份买的 mbp ，在 6 月 5 号，今天送到了。本来的预期送达日期是 7 月 9 号，到 8 月底。\n我估摸着如果发布会发了新品就退换更合适的。但是，今天突然送到了。\n出于激动，我还拆开来看了下，14 寸 10 核 16G 内存 1T 硬盘的 mbp 。\n有一点点重，但是看起来倒是挺小巧的。观感还行，可是明天就是发布会了啊，明天应该不会有 M2 的 mbp 吧？有点害怕。</p>\n<p>大家有什么想法么？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1654308362, "replies": 33, "id": 857213}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1651385949", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1651385949", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 49081, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1651385949", "stars": 7844, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 538663, "username": "Chaconne", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Chaconne", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d6ae37d6db56fa6288b8b85408a9d706?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d6ae37d6db56fa6288b8b85408a9d706?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d6ae37d6db